The papers are organized into fourteen series:
Correspondence, 1970-1985;
Self-Evaluations, Progress Data, and Logs, 1970-1983;
Michigan Diabetes Research and Training Center (MDRTC), 1976-1986;
Diabetes Center Unit (DCU), 1975-1983
University of Michigan Hospitals, Early Diabetes Program, 1970-1976;
University of Michigan Hospitals, Clinical Nurse Specialists (CNS), 1971-1983;
University of Michigan Hospitals, Nursing Services, 1975-1979;
Professional Activities, 1973-1988
Photographs
Medical Nursing Area Meetings, 1979-1984
Diabetes Patient Education Program, DCU, 1973-1983;
Educational Service for Nursing (ESN) 1978-1985
School f Nursing and Nursing Services, U-M Hospitals, 1980-1992
Patient Log Book, 1972-1982
